{"tid":2116220,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東區醫院一名外科病房男病人初步確診","createTime":"2020-07-20T04:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T04:32:35.000Z","uid":301585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7d8aed266e0d94a901d12b5f352301b46060d407","tid":2116220,"uid":301585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T04:31:36.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】消息指，東區醫院一名入住外科病房多日的男病人，院方獲悉他的家人確診感染新型冠狀病毒後，為患者檢測，亦初步確診。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，一名54歲男患者上星期經急症室入住東區醫院E8外科病房，進行盲腸炎手術，手術過程涉及全身麻醉及插喉，醫護有穿保護裝備。<br />\n<br />\n病人手術後一直留在外科病房，院方其後獲悉患者有家人確診感染新型冠狀病毒，之後為患者進行病毒檢測，初步呈陽性反應，在昨日轉送隔離病房。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，患者病毒量高。據了解，患者曾入住的病房需要封閉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=398628\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D398628&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=e5494f81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D398628&h=be0c9b95\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=398628</a>"},{"pid":"18c6674f8a113743f6c3a008f64e8ca2408532b3","tid":2116220,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T04:32:35.000Z","msg":"仆街了"}]}